    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "falling apart sounds like it would just be more pain. what if there's nothing to fall back on? what if the \"letting go\" part isn't about a new version of me, but just about the fact that there is no point in staying? i feel like i'm just lingering in a room where the lights have already been turned off.",
